{%- comment -%}
Displays an error message describing a non-fatal page build error.

You can see all these errors on the command line after a
local site build using the _bin/site-build-errors.sh script.
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- assign message = include.message -%}
{% include notice class="error" glyph="&#10060;" highlight-color="red" content=message %}

